2
00:00:23,540 --> 00:00:27,570
ظآزAlways stumbling upon
my little secretsظآز

3
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:31,990
ظآزFalling on my brows, my lashes,
even the strands by my mouthظآز

4
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:36,660
ظآزLike my favorite kitten
on a rainy spring afternoonظآز

5
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:41,320
ظآزHey, you, you, you,
why is it you again?ظآز

6
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:45,110
ظآزYou effortlessly awaken
my protective instinctsظآز

7
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:49,450
ظآزHitting all my little thoughts,
my doubts, and my temperظآز

8
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:54,300
ظآزLike my favorite beer and fried chicken
in autumn, or spicy boiled fish in winterظآز

9
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:58,770
ظآزWhy is it you again?
That sweet way you speakظآز

10
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,080
ظآزAs if the whole world knows
my mind is full of youظآز

11
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:07,530
ظآزWhy is it still you?
That secret smile behind your cool facadeظآز

12
00:01:07,730 --> 00:01:11,760
ظآزI might as well play along.
Let me protect youظآز

13
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:16,190
ظآزWhy is it always you?
The smile at the corner of your lipsظآز

14
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:20,590
