"I like you. I only like you."ظآز

15
00:01:29,530 --> 00:01:33,220
ظآزBefore I knew it, the words blurted out,
"I like you. I only like you."ظآز

16
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:34,040
=Love Has Fireworks=

17
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:34,861
(Based on "Investment Men and Women"
by Hong Er on Jinjiang Literature City)

18
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,980
=Episode 10=

19
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:54,230
Qian Fei.

20
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:54,870
Ms. Fang.

21
00:01:54,911 --> 00:01:56,960
The files you brought back
from Chengdu are crucial.

22
00:01:56,977 --> 00:01:58,890
They're vital to our partnership
with Shanlifang.

23
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:01,030
But you might not grasp
the full implications just yet.

24
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,900
So today, learn and observe more,
and talk less.

25
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:03,760
Preferably, don't talk.

26
00:02:03,770 --> 00:02:05,044
- Boss.
- Okay, I understand.

27
00:02:05,066 --> 00:02:07,430
Shanlifang Hotel Group has falsified data.

28
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,120
Ms. Fang.

29
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,390
We're just going to let it slide?

30
00:02:09,422 --> 00:02:11,590
- So glad you could come.
- Sorry to keep you waiting.

31
00:02:11,622 --> 00:02:12,670
Sorry to keep you waiting.

32
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,150
Not at all.

33
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,380
I'm delighted that you're here.

34
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,620
- Mr. Wu.
- This way, please.

35
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,080
Mr. Li.

36
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,750
Ms. Fang.

37
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,710
Come on, welcome.

38
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,590
Please.

39
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,120
Come on.

40
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,710
Come on in.

41
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:26,620
(Shanlifang Hotel Group)

42
00:02:26,666 --> 00:02:27,470
Welcome.

43
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:29,230
We've been looking forward
to your arrival.

44
00:02:29,244 --> 00:02:30,488
This way, please. This way.

45
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,000
Mr. Li,

46
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:34,560
this is your office.

47
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:35,870
Nice.

48
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,430
Come on. This way, please.

49
00:02:37,533 --> 00:02:38,844
This is the conference room.

50
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,240
The pantry.

51
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,190
Ms. Fang.

52
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:42,960
Not bad.

53
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,590
Your office is over here.

54
00:02:45,444 --> 00:02:46,777
It's more impressive than mine.

55
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,520
What do you think? Take a look.

56
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:51,400
This is the independent office space
we've set up

57
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,640
for the joint sponsorship team.

58
00:02:52,650 --> 00:02:54,200
Let us know if you need anything else.

59
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,222
Don't hesitate to ask.

60
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,711
We will spare no expense

61
00:02:56,777 --> 00:02:59,622
to ensure you have everything you need
for the battle ahead.

62
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,550
Before Shanlifang Hotel Group's
review meeting,

63
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,800
it's going to be a test
for all three of us.

64
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,080
Be well-prepared, stay relaxed,

65
00:03:06,155 --> 00:03:08,533
and professionally
manage the book building. No problem.

66
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:11,240
Your professional capabilities
are beyond question.

67
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,150
You're both benchmarks in the industry.

68
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,190
So,

69
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:17,150
we'll follow your lead.

70
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,240
As for the work itself,

71
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:21,560
once you've settled in,

72
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,840
we can coordinate as we go.

73
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,630
Okay.

74
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,630
It's getting late.

75
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,430
Let's head to the banquet hall
for lunch.

76
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,630
We can talk while we eat, alright?
Let's go.

77
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,190
After you.

78
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:31,030
Come on.

79
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,150
Great.

80
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,280
Not bad, right?

81
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,150
Now that everyone's here,

82
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,080
on behalf of the group,

83
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,470
I'd like to welcome you all
to Shanlifang.

84
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,310
Shanlifang's IPO

85
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,710
will depend
on everyone's close cooperation.

86
00:03:48,650 --> 00:03:50,177
I'd like to propose a toast to you all.

87
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:54,870
After this drink,

88
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,520
we'll be fighting side by side.

89
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,710
Although Mr. Wu's hospitality
is hard to refuse,

90
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:01,960
we have an important meeting
after this meal.

91
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,560
So let's not overdo it with the drinks.

92
00:04:04,844 --> 00:04:05,840
To a successful project.

93
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:16,000
Mr. Liao won't be at the meeting
this afternoon.

94
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,460
Ms. Liao will be attending instead.

95
00:04:18,511 --> 00:04:19,600
Mr. Liao isn't coming?

96
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:21,380
Something came up
for Mr. Liao unexpectedly.

97
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:23,240
He asked Ms. Liao to attend
in his place.

98
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:27,310
I heard this Ms. Liao
is young and beautiful,

99
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,750
and also very capable. Is that right?

100
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,680
Yes, yes.

101
00:04:31,290 --> 00:04:34,120
Ms. Liao is just as driven

102
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,380
as Mr. Liao was in his youth.

103
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:42,070
Sorry, I'm late.

104
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:48,120
Ms. Liao, it's great
you could make time to come.

105
00:04:48,244 --> 00:04:49,600
Let me make an introduction.

106
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:52,120
This is Shanlifang Hotel Group's

107
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:52,933
Vice President Liao.

108
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:53,830
Hello.

109
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:54,830
And this is...

110
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,120
Wu, does she really
need an introduction?

111
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,630
Director Fang of Hejing Securities.

112
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:00,160
Who in Shanghai doesn't know her?

113
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,480
You flatter me.

114
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:03,870
Now that I've finally met you,

115
00:05:04,022 --> 00:05:06,466
you're even younger
and more beautiful than I imagined.

116
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,300
This is...

117
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:11,510
Mr. Li.

118
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,360
Ms. Liao.

119
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,040
My dad often praises you to me.

120
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,360
He tells me to learn from you.

121
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,950
Now, I finally have the chance.

122
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,430
You're too kind, Ms. Liao.

123
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,310
We at Zhizhong are here
to be of service.

124
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,870
Here's to a pleasant collaboration.

125
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:23,630
Absolutely.

126
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,980
The person who will be liaising with you

127
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:28,920
is our group's Chief Financial Officer,

128
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,860
Mr. Wang Ruohai.

129
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,510
He'll be in charge of coordinating

130
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,888
with the joint sponsorship team.

131
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,800
Hello.

132
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,430
Hello.

133
00:05:42,488 --> 00:05:43,190
Great to meet you.

134
00:05:43,222 --> 00:05:44,070
Great to meet you.

135
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,870
I'll be counting
on your support from now on.

136
00:05:48,422 --> 00:05:50,360
Let's not stand around.
Please, have a seat.

137
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:50,720
Okay.

138
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,088
We're all one big family now.

139
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:57,800
Ruohai.

140
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,270
This Silver Cod
with Black Truffle and Lily Bulbs

141
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:02,311
is a new dish developed
by our Chinese cuisine chef.

142
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:03,160
I heard the cod

143
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,750
was just flown in today.

144
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,000
I can't eat seafood today.

145
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,070
Try it for me.

146
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,390
Come, Ms. Fang.

147
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:14,480
A toast to you.

148
00:06:14,822 --> 00:06:16,066
I was just about to toast you.

149
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:16,480
Come on.

150
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,688
To a pleasant collaboration.

151
00:06:18,733 --> 00:06:19,933
To a pleasant collaboration.

152
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,390
Mr. Wang.

153
00:06:21,711 --> 00:06:23,200
I'd like to toast the two of you.

154
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:25,720
I hope our project goes smoothly.

155
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,100
And please, guide us along the way.

156
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:27,870
Of course.

157
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,070
Cheers.

158
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,680
Come on.

159
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,430
Ms. Liao.

160
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:32,777
Drink a little less.
We still have work this afternoon.

161
00:06:36,165 --> 00:06:36,800
Thanks.

162
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,510
To you.

163
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,470
A pleasant collaboration.

164
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,688
To a pleasant collaboration.

165
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,270
Thank you.

166
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:48,870
Qian Fei.

167
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,510
Mr. Wang,
who is sitting across from you,

168
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,040
in our future work,

169
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,390
we'll be dealing with him a lot.

170
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,510
In a bit,

171
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,933
go and propose a toast to him.

172
00:07:09,933 --> 00:07:11,580
(Pretentious Li:
If you don't want to go, don't go.)

173
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,480
Ms. Liao, come on.

174
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:18,190
I must toast you.

175
00:07:18,688 --> 00:07:19,920
It's our first time meeting.

176
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,630
I'll toast you.

177
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:24,620
(Qian Fei: So you knew all along.)

178
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,040
Madam.

179
00:07:30,088 --> 00:07:32,160
Right, it's not convenient
for me to drink today.

180
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,270
No problem.

181
00:07:33,355 --> 00:07:35,088
Let's collaborate more in the future.

182
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,630
Mr. Wang, I'd like to toast you.

183
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,360
Wishing you a successful career
and a bright future.

184
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:47,390
And a happy life.

185
00:07:48,088 --> 00:07:50,111
I'll drink up.
You can drink as you please.

186
00:07:50,622 --> 00:07:51,911
Let's both drink as we please...

187
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:01,480
Okay, then please have a seat.

188
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,630
Ms. Liao, I'd like to toast you as well.

189
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:07,830
Ms. Fang, this is...

190
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,510
This is my assistant, Qian Fei.

191
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,390
Didn't you notice
Ms. Liao isn't drinking?

192
00:08:13,577 --> 00:08:15,644
I'll drink up.
You can drink as you please.

193
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,830
Alright, it's the thought that counts.

194
00:08:24,977 --> 00:08:26,370
We still have work this afternoon.

195
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,390
Okay.

196
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:29,070
I'm happy today, Ms. Fang.

197
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,750
It's my first time meeting Ms. Liao

198
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:33,670
and Mr. Wang.

199
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,720
So I'm very happy today.

200
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:41,390
In this moment,
I'd really like to propose a toast.

201
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,577
I'll propose a toast.

202
00:08:43,355 --> 00:08:45,240
I suggest, since we have work
this afternoon,

203
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,360
we don't drink so much.

204
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,822
How about we use tea instead of wine?

205
00:08:47,844 --> 00:08:48,390
Excellent.

206
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:48,790
Right?

207
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,133
That's an excellent suggestion.

208
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,870
Excellent. Come on.

209
00:08:53,044 --> 00:08:53,910
No more drinking.

210
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,360
This...

211
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,480
Right?

212
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,840
- Cheers.
- Then let's hope our work ahead

213
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,120
goes smoothly.
To a pleasant collaboration.

214
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:03,670
It's all in the tea.

215
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,800
Thanks for your hard work.

216
00:09:04,810 --> 00:09:06,044
Thank you for your hard work.

217
00:09:12,977 --> 00:09:14,030
Please, have a seat.

218
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,030
Mr. Li.

219
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,550
I heard you made a special trip

220
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,340
to Shanlifang's old headquarters
in Chengdu.

221
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,533
That's real dedication.

222
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,870
Let me toast to you.

223
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,670
Thank you, Ms. Liao.

224
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,720
You're too kind.

225
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,080
It's what we're supposed to do.

226
00:09:38,311 --> 00:09:40,510
Did you learn anything
from your trip to Chengdu?

227
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,750
We learned quite a lot.

228
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,480
Did Ms. Qian go along as well?

229
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:50,360
Qian Fei, have you had
too much to drink?

230
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:52,240
Why don't you go rest for a bit?

231
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:54,840
I'm not drunk

232
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,200
and I don't need to rest.

233
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,600
Ms. Liao,

234
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,630
Mr. Wang.

235
00:09:58,790 --> 00:10:00,030
Shanlifang Hotel Group,

236
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:01,720
during its pre-IPO preparations,

237
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:05,030
provided our sponsorship team
and the audit department

238
00:10:05,270 --> 00:10:08,240
with many illogical financial statements

239
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,320
and concealed a lot of real data.

240
00:10:10,829 --> 00:10:13,429
Especially regarding intangible assets,

241
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,933
there are major discrepancies.

242
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:17,200
May I ask why that is?

243
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,790
What did you say?

244
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,960
According to CSRC and legal regulations,

245
00:10:25,133 --> 00:10:27,000
a company
that severely falsifies its assets

246
00:10:27,288 --> 00:10:28,750
is not allowed to pass the review.

247
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:32,600
Is Mr. Wang unaware of this,

248
00:10:32,644 --> 00:10:34,622
since this is your first time
on an IPO project?

249
00:10:50,488 --> 00:10:51,511
Here's the thing.

250
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:52,440
Um...

251
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:55,000
If the accounts are falsified,

252
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:57,030
even if the IPO is successful,

253
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,550
you can still be held accountable.

254
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,550
But the good thing is,

255
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,480
we discovered this very early.

256
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,080
So as long as the client provides

257
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:08,030
the real and complete financial data,

258
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:10,270
there's still plenty of time
to fix everything.

259
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,670
Don't worry, let's just eat and drink.

260
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,200
Please.

261
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:18,030
Let's just enjoy our meal.

262
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,320
I'm sorry.

263
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:24,320
I sent Qian Fei to Chengdu
to be Mr. Li's assistant,

264
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,080
but I didn't expect
that in just a few days,

265
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,670
she'd be poached by Zhizhong.

266
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:31,200
See? Mr. Li is just that charming.

267
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,390
Ms. Fang.

268
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,200
Alright.

269
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,910
Well said, Ms. Fang.

270
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,270
Brilliant.

271
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,120
Um, that's not...

272
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,390
Ms. Liao, here's the thing.

273
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:45,630
Actually, regarding what Qian Fei said,

274
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:48,666
I was going to bring it up with you
during our meeting this afternoon.

275
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,360
This kind of issue must be raised.

276
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,440
But I didn't expect this...

277
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,120
But it's okay.

278
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:56,870
Sooner or later,

279
00:11:57,022 --> 00:11:58,911
it had to be said at the meeting anyway.

280
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,480
Let's eat first.

281
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:10,860
(Shanlifang Hotel Group,
Conference Room)

282
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,000
2022, 202...

283
00:12:37,711 --> 00:12:39,000
Alright, let's continue.

284
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,440
Ms. Liao,

285
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,080
I'm sorry.

286
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:55,790
I really don't know why

287
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:57,550
Qian Fei is on the sponsorship team.

288
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:58,720
But don't worry.

289
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:01,060
This was all my fault.

290
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:03,066
I'll do everything I can
to make up for it.

291
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,510
I promise it won't affect
the company's IPO.

292
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:11,270
Come here.

293
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,510
I told you.

294
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:27,220
Just call me Shiyu when we're alone.

295
00:13:27,780 --> 00:13:29,020
Why do you keep forgetting?

296
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:38,500
I'm tired.

297
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:40,100
Give me a massage.

298
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,220
We're still at the office.

299
00:13:45,180 --> 00:13:46,860
There aren't even any cameras here.

300
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,340
Who's going to see?

301
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:56,540
Do you know this place better than I do?

302
00:14:07,195 --> 00:14:08,060
Mr. Li.

303
00:14:08,155 --> 00:14:10,311
- I'll get going.
- Okay, thank you for your hard work.

304
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:17,180
Qian Fei.

305
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:21,140
Come to my office at five.

306
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:24,980
Boss.

307
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:27,220
That old fox, Fang Yun,
is really something.

308
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:30,180
I can't believe she kicked
the ball back into our court.

309
00:14:30,333 --> 00:14:31,500
But we're the bigger men.

310
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:32,660
We won't stoop to their level.

311
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:36,180
But I have to say,
you were amazing in the meeting today.

312
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:38,540
Reasonable, well-argued,
and perfectly composed.

313
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,100
Boss.

314
00:14:40,755 --> 00:14:42,720
I'm talking to you.
What are you thinking about?

315
00:14:42,755 --> 00:14:43,488
It's nothing.

316
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:46,020
Then let's head back to Zhizhong?

317
00:14:47,088 --> 00:14:49,222
You go ahead.
I still have something to do.

318
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:52,488
I'll head back first, then.

319
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:01,940
(Qian Fei, oh, Qian Fei.)

320
00:15:02,444 --> 00:15:04,666
(How could you lose
your composure like that today?)

321
00:15:05,933 --> 00:15:07,111
They are here.

322
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:09,580
Ruohai, I can't eat seafood today.

323
00:15:09,688 --> 00:15:10,660
You can try some for me.

324
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:11,660
Okay.

325
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,620
(Haven't you gotten over
that scumbag already?)

326
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:28,660
(Is he even worth all this?)

327
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:31,900
(Qian Fei, snap out of it.)

328
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:43,100
(Shanlifang Hotel Group)

329
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:43,900
Ms. Qian.

330
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:48,140
Ms. Liao, what can I do for you?

331
00:15:49,010 --> 00:15:51,770
I heard you were doing odd jobs
in the back end of the investment bank.

332
00:15:51,780 --> 00:15:53,360
And now, you've joined the project team.

333
00:15:53,370 --> 00:15:55,340
You're participating
in our Shanlifang Hotel Group's

334
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,300
IPO project.

335
00:15:56,500 --> 00:15:58,260
That shows you're quite capable.

336
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:03,600
I also hope you can keep your personal
and professional lives separate.

337
00:16:04,444 --> 00:16:05,980
You really think too highly of me.

338
00:16:06,180 --> 00:16:09,100
I just try to do my own job well
within the limited time I have.

339
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:11,380
Satisfying my superiors
and clients is enough for me.

340
00:16:11,555 --> 00:16:12,800
As for other personal matters,

341
00:16:12,844 --> 00:16:14,610
I simply don't have time
to think about them.

342
00:16:14,622 --> 00:16:15,933
You are exceptionally capable

343
00:16:15,977 --> 00:16:17,180
and even have a sharp tongue.

344
00:16:17,660 --> 00:16:19,220
We already saw that at the dining table.

345
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:22,020
Right, Ruohai?

346
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:27,140
I've known Qian Fei for many years,

347
00:16:27,644 --> 00:16:29,980
but it's our first time
working together professionally.

348
00:16:30,355 --> 00:16:31,740
However, I trust her abilities.

349
00:16:32,222 --> 00:16:34,140
I'm sure she's more than qualified
for this job.

350
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,340
Well then,

351
00:16:35,980 --> 00:16:36,980
I'll be waiting to see.

352
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:38,540
Let's see what other

353
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,177
surprises you have in store for me.

354
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:42,460
Shanlifang Hotel Group

355
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:44,360
is a client we serve
to the best of our ability.

356
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:45,940
Surprising you is not my goal.

357
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:48,620
Helping Mr. Wang fill in the gaps

358
00:16:48,711 --> 00:16:51,060
and participating in
Shanlifang Hotel Group's successful IPO

359
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:52,220
is my honor.

360
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:59,140
Then let me say a few words
in a personal capacity.

361
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:02,460
You've always worked in the back end.

362
00:17:02,470 --> 00:17:04,730
Now that you've gotten a chance
to join the project team,

363
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:05,700
you should cherish it.

364
00:17:06,777 --> 00:17:08,540
Well, thank you for the reminder,
Mr. Wang.

365
00:17:08,977 --> 00:17:11,100
Then let me also respond
in a personal capacity.

366
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:13,660
Wasting a few years
isn't actually that scary.

367
00:17:13,933 --> 00:17:16,780
You only realize how precious
chances are after you've wasted them.

368
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:18,820
Who hasn't run into a scumbag before?

369
00:17:26,755 --> 00:17:28,977
The marketing department meeting
is about to start.

370
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:30,300
Let's go.

371
00:17:37,020 --> 00:17:37,700
Ms. Fang,

372
00:17:38,133 --> 00:17:39,380
I've found out everything.

373
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:42,940
That Wang Ruohai
is Qian Fei's ex-boyfriend.

374
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:46,540
He used to work at Nalan Maide Bank.

375
00:17:46,780 --> 00:17:48,780
The staff there all know Qian Fei.

376
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:52,180
I heard they even bought a house
for their marriage

377
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:53,533
and booked the wedding banquet.

378
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:55,355
They were just short
of having the wedding.

379
00:17:59,740 --> 00:18:00,740
So you're saying

380
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:02,500
Wang Ruohai

381
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,980
left Qian Fei because of Liao Shiyu?

382
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,380
Looks like it.

383
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,580
Qian Fei was desperate to get into

384
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:13,460
the Shanlifang Hotel Group project team.

385
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:17,620
She must be trying
to drag Wang Ruohai down with her

386
00:18:17,733 --> 00:18:18,860
for mutual destruction.

387
00:18:19,260 --> 00:18:21,820
Why else would she cause
such a huge mess?

388
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,700
Is Qian Fei that calculating?

389
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:33,210
Who knows?

390
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:36,980
But having Qian Fei on our project team

391
00:18:37,111 --> 00:18:38,600
is a disaster waiting to happen.

392
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:45,420
I'm actually quite interested
to see how this drama unfolds.

393
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:13,060
(Grand Chancellor: Are you busy?)

394
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:44,900
(Grand Chancellor: It's okay not to
reply. Just making my presence known.)

395
00:20:01,700 --> 00:20:06,780
(Hejing Securities Co., Ltd.)

396
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:12,260
Okay.

397
00:20:12,288 --> 00:20:13,155
I'll leave it to you.

398
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,580
I'll take over this afternoon, okay?

399
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:15,380
Sure.

400
00:20:29,380 --> 00:20:31,100
(Security Monitor Wall)

401
00:20:34,980 --> 00:20:38,020
(Lobby, Entrance 1)

402
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:40,140
(Hejing Securities Co., Ltd.)

403
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,740
(Hejing Securities Co., Ltd.)

404
00:21:15,900 --> 00:21:16,700
Ms. Fang.

405
00:21:22,740 --> 00:21:24,860
Ms. Fang, I came to apologize to you.

406
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:26,340
I'm truly sorry.

407
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,940
You always told me

408
00:21:28,340 --> 00:21:29,980
to observe more and learn more,

409
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:31,900
to speak less,
or better yet, not at all.

410
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:33,260
But this time, I still...

411
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:34,500
You're almost 30, aren't you?

412
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:36,220
How are you worse than an intern?

413
00:21:37,111 --> 00:21:38,990
You've been in the workplace
for so many years.

414
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,260
You can't even control yourself.

415
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:42,355
I'm sorry. I was too impulsive

416
00:21:42,422 --> 00:21:43,600
and reckless this time.

417
00:21:43,610 --> 00:21:45,700
I've caused you and the company
such a negative impact.

418
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:47,590
I've also affected your work
and everyone else's.

419
00:21:47,620 --> 00:21:50,140
I'm willing
to make a public self-criticism.

420
00:21:50,580 --> 00:21:51,820
I hope you can forgive me.

421
00:21:52,220 --> 00:21:53,300
Many things

422
00:21:53,844 --> 00:21:55,460
can't be solved with a self-criticism.

423
00:21:55,780 --> 00:21:58,660
Li Yifei was merciful today.
He didn't kick us while we were down.

424
00:21:58,660 --> 00:22:00,500
Otherwise, our company, Hejing,

425
00:22:00,533 --> 00:22:02,444
would have been ruined by you alone.

426
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:04,380
We could have been kicked off
the project team.

427
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:05,311
Do you realize that?

428
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:07,540
Do you think a self-criticism
can solve everything?

429
00:22:08,420 --> 00:22:09,940
I know how serious this was.

430
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,140
But I still hope

431
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:12,620
you can give me one last chance.

432
00:22:12,780 --> 00:22:14,220
You know how much effort

433
00:22:14,500 --> 00:22:16,540
I put into returning to Hejing.

434
00:22:17,133 --> 00:22:19,260
Don't talk to me
about how much you've put in.

435
00:22:19,420 --> 00:22:20,644
Who here hasn't put in a lot?

436
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:22,420
To land this Shanlifang project,

437
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:24,980
do you know how many sleepless nights
the entire team had?

438
00:22:25,100 --> 00:22:26,288
How much overtime we worked?

439
00:22:26,466 --> 00:22:29,100
Does anyone in our investment
banking industry not make sacrifices?

440
00:22:29,220 --> 00:22:30,780
Does anyone put in less effort?

441
00:22:31,022 --> 00:22:32,990
And you think what you've done
is so remarkable?

442
00:22:33,140 --> 00:22:34,020
You're not even close.

443
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:36,620
How can I dare to use someone like you?

444
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:38,580
Ms. Fang, I...

445
00:22:41,580 --> 00:22:41,980
Mr. Li.

446
00:22:42,740 --> 00:22:43,780
Did I come at a bad time?

447
00:22:43,780 --> 00:22:44,220
No.

448
00:22:44,220 --> 00:22:45,380
Please, Mr. Li, come on in.

449
00:22:45,380 --> 00:22:45,900
Ms. Fang.

450
00:22:46,888 --> 00:22:47,940
I brought you some apples

451
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:49,488
grown by my relatives back home.

452
00:22:49,577 --> 00:22:50,380
They're organic.

453
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:51,060
Thank you.

454
00:22:51,060 --> 00:22:52,180
This is such a rare treat.

455
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:52,980
Please, have a seat.

456
00:22:53,020 --> 00:22:53,220
Okay.

457
00:22:53,230 --> 00:22:53,880
You can go now.

458
00:22:54,266 --> 00:22:55,220
It's alright, Qian Fei.

459
00:22:56,260 --> 00:22:57,220
Why don't you listen in?

460
00:23:02,780 --> 00:23:03,380
Ms. Fang,

461
00:23:05,140 --> 00:23:06,060
to be honest with you,

462
00:23:06,622 --> 00:23:08,400
I've run into a bit of trouble lately.

463
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:10,580
What kind of trouble?

464
00:23:11,340 --> 00:23:12,540
Don't laugh when I tell you.

465
00:23:12,577 --> 00:23:14,155
It's about my assistant, Zhao De.

466
00:23:14,180 --> 00:23:15,111
You remember him, right?

467
00:23:15,222 --> 00:23:17,355
He's got a bunch of things going on
at Zhizhong now.

468
00:23:17,860 --> 00:23:19,060
He's completely swamped.

469
00:23:19,340 --> 00:23:20,980
He has no time for my matters at all.

470
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:23,220
Just when we're short-staffed,

471
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,260
he pulls this on me.

472
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:26,220
I'm really...

473
00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:28,340
Sometimes, I really envy you.

474
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,780
You're surrounded by this huge crowd...

475
00:23:30,888 --> 00:23:32,820
No, I mean, you're surrounded
by so much talent.

476
00:23:32,866 --> 00:23:34,555
Every single one of them is competent.

477
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:36,620
When I think about my own situation,

478
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:37,460
I just feel...

479
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:38,900
I'm so frustrated. I really am.

480
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:40,340
I'm truly envious.

481
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:43,020
I understand.
You're short-staffed, right?

482
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:45,780
Why haven't you requested someone
from Zhizhong?

483
00:23:46,020 --> 00:23:47,020
I'd like to.

484
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:49,820
But ever since working with you,

485
00:23:49,820 --> 00:23:51,933
when I look at the people
at Zhizhong, I just...

486
00:23:53,300 --> 00:23:54,820
It's too difficult. It really is.

487
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,700
Are you suggesting...

488
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:05,900
Is there anyone at Hejing

489
00:24:06,711 --> 00:24:07,933
you think could help you out?

490
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:10,100
People like Dacui

491
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:12,180
or Daisy, I wouldn't dare ask for them.

492
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:13,380
They're truly very capable.

493
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:15,660
I'm just looking
for a special assistant.

494
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:18,460
It would be a waste
of their great talent,

495
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:19,100
right?

496
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:21,140
I think someone like...

497
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:22,140
Well,

498
00:24:22,666 --> 00:24:24,266
someone like Qian Fei, for example,

499
00:24:26,222 --> 00:24:27,180
with average abilities,

500
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:28,780
would be fine

501
00:24:28,888 --> 00:24:29,620
as an assistant.

502
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:32,580
Would you mind letting her
work as my special assistant

503
00:24:32,580 --> 00:24:33,860
while we're collaborating?

504
00:24:34,260 --> 00:24:35,200
What do you think?

505
00:25:02,820 --> 00:25:07,300
(Hejing Securities Co., Ltd.)

506
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:09,700
Hello.

507
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:12,660
Hello, this is building security.

508
00:25:12,780 --> 00:25:14,022
Excuse me, after 3:30 PM,

509
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,000
have you been the one on duty here
the whole time?

510
00:25:16,020 --> 00:25:17,260
Yes. What's wrong?

511
00:25:17,577 --> 00:25:18,420
Here's the thing.

512
00:25:18,466 --> 00:25:20,311
Take a look. Do you know this person?

513
00:25:22,460 --> 00:25:23,820
Why did he follow me here?

514
00:25:24,860 --> 00:25:25,820
He's still in the lobby.

515
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:28,620
If you feel that he poses a threat
to your personal safety,

516
00:25:28,733 --> 00:25:30,933
you can leave
through the back door after work.

517
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:32,940
Okay, thank you.

518
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:33,900
Sure. You're welcome.

519
00:25:40,311 --> 00:25:41,900
(He doesn't need a special assistant.)

520
00:25:42,044 --> 00:25:43,780
(He clearly just wants me
to run errands.)

521
00:25:44,244 --> 00:25:46,020
(And what's with the pour-over coffee?)

522
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,460
(So pretentious.)

523
00:26:09,090 --> 00:26:15,540
ظآزWhenever I look upظآز

524
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:23,170
ظآزI meet your gaze, those eyesظآز

525
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:30,310
ظآزI wish to hold on to that light of joyظآز

526
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:37,780
ظآزAnd embrace that fleeting happinessظآز

527
00:26:39,110 --> 00:26:45,580
ظآزSometimes we cry, sometimes we laughظآز

