533
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,460
(Qian Fei,)

534
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:18,420
(this is reality.)

535
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:22,730
ظآزTo love or not to loveظآز

536
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:25,180
(Seeing a person clearly
through a different relationship.)

537
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:28,660
(This person was once
very important to me.)

538
00:27:30,140 --> 00:27:32,020
(But from now on,)

539
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:34,100
(he has nothing to do with me.)

540
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:39,377
(Shanlifang Hotel Group,
Director's Office)

541
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:45,520
ظآزI've never met a sea
as brilliant as youظآز

542
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:53,180
ظآزEvery minute is so colorfulظآز

543
00:27:54,030 --> 00:28:00,680
ظآزI've never known a love
as warm as yoursظآز

544
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:10,810
ظآزNothing more needs to be said,
I won't let go of youظآز

545
00:28:38,340 --> 00:28:40,660
ظآزThe rain keeps fallingظآز

546
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:44,740
ظآزThe atmosphere
isn't exactly harmoniousظآز

547
00:28:46,620 --> 00:28:47,900
It's pretty disharmonious.

548
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:52,180
You knew all along, didn't you?

549
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:58,133
Then why didn't you tell me sooner?

550
00:28:58,540 --> 00:29:00,260
I was protecting you, okay?

551
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:01,460
Tell me,

552
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,340
if you had known earlier

553
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:05,500
that Wang Ruohai was
Financial Director at Shanlifang,

554
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:08,010
would you have tried so hard
to get back to Hejing

555
00:29:08,140 --> 00:29:09,377
and join the project team?

556
00:29:09,540 --> 00:29:09,980
Would you?

557
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:25,088
Let me tell you something.

558
00:29:26,688 --> 00:29:28,700
I've been in investment banking
for so many years,

559
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,980
so I've met my fair share of people.

560
00:29:33,088 --> 00:29:35,688
I genuinely think you have
what it takes for this line of work.

561
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:39,340
I just value talent.

562
00:29:40,340 --> 00:29:43,060
I don't want to see you give up

563
00:29:43,060 --> 00:29:44,580
an important career opportunity

564
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:46,660
and a turning point in your life

565
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:48,555
for some trivial,
insignificant relationship.

566
00:29:50,444 --> 00:29:53,000
Also, as your master,
let me give you another piece of truth.

567
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:57,980
Don't value relationships
above all else.

568
00:29:58,220 --> 00:30:00,300
In this world, only your work

569
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:02,700
will not betray your effort and passion.

570
00:30:05,300 --> 00:30:07,180
I've already moved on.

571
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:12,420
Besides, he has someone new now.

572
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:14,220
I respect his choice.

573
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:18,780
At least I know

574
00:30:19,260 --> 00:30:20,980
that I once loved with all my heart.

575
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:22,660
That's enough.

576
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:25,900
Are you a woodpecker?

577
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:27,500
You're so stubborn.

578
00:30:28,244 --> 00:30:29,288
If you had really moved on,

579
00:30:29,290 --> 00:30:31,540
would you have reacted extremely
in the banquet hall today

580
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:33,288
and exposed
Shanlifang's financial problems?

581
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:35,580
Well, how was I supposed to know

582
00:30:35,580 --> 00:30:37,060
I'd run into the two of them?

583
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:39,460
I have moved on.

584
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:40,900
But when I saw them together,

585
00:30:40,900 --> 00:30:42,820
I just... My anger just flared up.

586
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:45,300
I wasn't thinking straight.

587
00:30:45,420 --> 00:30:46,500
It's only human.

588
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:51,500
I had to turn my anger into courage

589
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,180
to say it all in one go.

590
00:30:58,100 --> 00:30:58,700
That's why,

591
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:02,100
whenever I see you not thinking clearly,

592
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:02,980
I'm just glad

593
00:31:03,900 --> 00:31:05,740
my parents didn't raise a fool.

594
00:31:07,511 --> 00:31:08,444
Think about it.

595
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,300
Today, in front of so many people,

596
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,933
you went against Ms. Fang's wishes.

597
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:14,420
She could have fired you in a heartbeat.

598
00:31:16,088 --> 00:31:18,155
You worked so hard
to get into this project team.

599
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,260
What now?

600
00:31:19,577 --> 00:31:20,460
Just a one-day tour?

601
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,980
Hurry up and thank your master.

602
00:31:28,622 --> 00:31:30,355
It's all thanks to me
that you were saved.

603
00:31:30,980 --> 00:31:31,900
Okay.

604
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:32,900
Thank you.

605
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:35,940
Thank you.

606
00:31:37,740 --> 00:31:38,580
That's more like it.

607
00:31:40,150 --> 00:31:41,980
Also, starting today,

608
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:44,580
you're my special assistant.

609
00:31:47,900 --> 00:31:48,700
From now on,

610
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:50,888
you have to listen to me.

611
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:54,540
Only at the company.

612
00:31:54,740 --> 00:31:55,740
Only for work.

613
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:57,420
Outside of work, I'm still your master.

614
00:31:58,420 --> 00:32:00,260
Once a master, always a father figure.

615
00:32:00,377 --> 00:32:02,400
You've been calling me "master"
for so many days.

616
00:32:02,410 --> 00:32:03,700
You expect me to just abandon you?

617
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,780
In your dreams.

618
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,500
You want to enslave me all day?

619
00:32:07,620 --> 00:32:08,980
Don't say that about me.

620
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:11,220
You're speaking my mind.

621
00:32:13,355 --> 00:32:14,740
Well, you're overthinking it.

622
00:32:14,820 --> 00:32:16,780
You think just because
you're my temporary boss,

623
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:18,260
I wouldn't dare make you move out?

624
00:32:19,111 --> 00:32:21,666
Whether I move out or not
depends on the contract, right?

625
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:24,460
Work is work,
and living together is living together.

626
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:26,500
Let's not mix them all up.

627
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:28,740
You'd better not.

628
00:32:29,340 --> 00:32:30,660
That mouth of yours

629
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:31,860
is always yapping.

630
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:36,540
It doesn't hurt to listen more,
you know?

631
00:32:37,780 --> 00:32:38,340
Fine.

632
00:32:38,740 --> 00:32:40,900
Looks like I gave the apples away
for nothing today.

633
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:44,140
Where did you get those apples anyway?

634
00:32:46,020 --> 00:32:47,300
From the supermarket downstairs.

635
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:48,980
I knew it.

636
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:51,860
But... But it's really organic.

637
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:52,820
I was not lying.

638
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:54,300
Okay.

639
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:56,420
Farewell.

640
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,500
Farewell?

641
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,460
So dramatic.

642
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:02,460
So childish.

643
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:50,580
So?

644
00:33:51,377 --> 00:33:53,220
Have you figured out
how to tell Qian Fei?

645
00:33:54,020 --> 00:33:55,460
We have to tell her sooner or later.

646
00:33:56,066 --> 00:33:58,380
Besides, she went to Shanlifang
for due diligence today.

647
00:33:58,660 --> 00:34:00,740
I think she must have seen
Wang Ruohai already.

648
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:02,420
And I believe she's already moved on.

649
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:14,500
You ordered so much.

650
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:14,860
Sit down.

651
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:17,580
Why are you all wet from the rain?
Here, dry yourself off.

652
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:20,060
I'm starving.

653
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:21,420
I knew you'd be hungry.

654
00:34:21,620 --> 00:34:23,620
Was your first day
of due diligence busy?

655
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:26,620
It's a long story.

656
00:34:28,740 --> 00:34:30,260
Can I just eat first?

657
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:31,400
Sure, dig in.

658
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,340
Okay, eat up.

659
00:34:37,288 --> 00:34:39,200
Why are you guys suddenly
treating me to a meal?

660
00:34:40,622 --> 00:34:42,555
Here to show off our lovey-dovey stuff.

661
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:44,660
You're exaggerating.

662
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:48,060
How can you still laugh?

663
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,340
Fei.

664
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:53,900
Actually, Jingjing and I are here today

665
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,140
to offer a humble apology.

666
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:57,820
What are you afraid of?

667
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,580
If she wants to kill us,
I'll take the blame.

668
00:35:00,711 --> 00:35:01,688
Just hurry up and say it.

669
00:35:01,690 --> 00:35:03,340
Don't think just
because she says nothing,

670
00:35:03,340 --> 00:35:04,580
- you can brush it off.
- Okay.

671
00:35:07,060 --> 00:35:09,420
Did you see

672
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:10,740
you-know-who today?

673
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:21,230
You two already knew

674
00:35:21,230 --> 00:35:23,230
that Wang Ruohai had gone to Shanlifang,
didn't you?

675
00:35:23,244 --> 00:35:25,220
Shanlifang is Xinxin Vision's
parent company.

676
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:27,540
Wang Ruohai just became
their new Finance Director.

677
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:29,740
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

678
00:35:30,180 --> 00:35:31,900
I was doing it for the sake
of your career.

679
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:33,820
What if you knew
that scumbag was at Shanlifang

680
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:35,580
and you didn't work hard

681
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:37,300
to get into Fang Yun's project team?

682
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:40,060
I was thinking of you.

683
00:35:40,460 --> 00:35:42,100
Don't you understand my good intentions?

684
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:57,780
How could I not understand you, silly?

685
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:00,866
It's a good thing you didn't tell me.

686
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:02,420
Otherwise, today,

687
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:04,711
I wouldn't have tried so hard
to get into that company.

688
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:06,580
Jingjing, you know me so well.

689
00:36:07,100 --> 00:36:07,740
See?

690
00:36:08,780 --> 00:36:10,100
Men are nothing.

691
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:12,340
To our mutual understanding.

692
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:13,260
Cheers.

693
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:18,140
Never try to guess
what a woman is thinking. Seriously.

694
00:36:19,066 --> 00:36:20,540
So you two treated me to dinner today

695
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:21,740
just for this?

696
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,860
There was no need.

697
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:26,140
Jingjing and I are so close.

698
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:27,820
We're not like those fake friends.

699
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,420
Great.

700
00:36:29,622 --> 00:36:31,022
Then we're splitting the bill today.

701
00:36:31,088 --> 00:36:31,822
No way.

702
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:34,422
I haven't said I forgive you yet.

703
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,540
You have to treat me.

704
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:36,380
Fine.

705
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:40,150
About Liao Shiyu and Wang Ruohai,

706
00:36:40,733 --> 00:36:42,577
they didn't give you
a hard time, did they?

707
00:36:42,580 --> 00:36:44,850
They're your clients now,
the daddies who pay the bills.

708
00:36:44,860 --> 00:36:46,100
I'm still a little worried.

709
00:36:47,666 --> 00:36:49,555
You said it yourself, they're
the daddies.

710
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:51,900
The client is always right.

711
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:55,180
They probably won't bother
picking on a small fry like me.

712
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,220
Don't worry.

713
00:36:57,860 --> 00:36:58,460
That's good.

714
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:01,140
If that woman, because of this,

715
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:03,180
makes things difficult for you
and fires you,

716
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:05,020
you have nothing to fear.

717
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:06,780
After we get married,

718
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,900
my husband will support me,
and I'll support you.

719
00:37:09,488 --> 00:37:11,580
"My husband will support me,
and I'll support you."

720
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:13,580
Wait.

721
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:14,990
No, the sentence before that.

722
00:37:15,020 --> 00:37:15,940
I can support you too.

723
00:37:18,180 --> 00:37:18,820
No, no.

724
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:21,780
"After we get married..."

725
00:37:21,780 --> 00:37:22,780
Wait, what do you mean?

726
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,060
It means...

727
00:37:27,140 --> 00:37:28,740
Yao Jingjing.

728
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:30,900
You guys are getting married?

729
00:37:31,155 --> 00:37:32,644
Didn't I tell you from the beginning

730
00:37:32,650 --> 00:37:34,530
that we were here
to display our affection today?

731
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:35,060
No.

732
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:36,740
When did you propose?

733
00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:41,580
Don't even get me started.

734
00:37:42,180 --> 00:37:44,180
You know, that day,
I had just bought the ring.

735
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,900
I hadn't even set up
the proposal scene yet.

736
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:46,940
I was in the shower,

737
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,060
and she found the ring.

738
00:37:48,177 --> 00:37:49,660
Let me tell you, in that situation,

739
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,444
if I hadn't proposed on the spot,

740
00:37:51,450 --> 00:37:53,060
she would have forced me to produce

741
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:54,300
the mistress she'd imagined.

742
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:57,500
So he, in his bathrobe and barefoot,

743
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:58,800
knelt on the floor and proposed.

744
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:00,820
There was zero romance.

745
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:03,940
That's incredible. Really.

746
00:38:04,010 --> 00:38:05,340
Too bad I wasn't there to see it.

747
00:38:06,822 --> 00:38:08,420
But who cares if it was romantic or not?

748
00:38:08,420 --> 00:38:10,020
Look, you're wearing the big ring.

749
00:38:10,133 --> 00:38:11,266
How is that not romantic?

750
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:14,140
I never thought the day would come

751
00:38:14,580 --> 00:38:16,900
when our Jingjing would be tamed.

752
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,660
I remember someone
used to always tell me

753
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:21,420
how terrible it was
to get married early.

754
00:38:21,688 --> 00:38:22,822
And look at you now.

755
00:38:23,822 --> 00:38:25,580
I, who desperately wanted
to get married,

756
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:27,100
can't get married anymore.

757
00:38:27,300 --> 00:38:28,140
But you,

758
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:30,222
you've hit the jackpot
in both career and love.

759
00:38:30,580 --> 00:38:31,660
Congratulations to you both.

760
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:33,060
Come on.

761
00:38:34,260 --> 00:38:36,377
I must toast you.
You've captured a siren.

762
00:38:36,466 --> 00:38:38,660
You've done a great service
to the people.

763
00:38:38,780 --> 00:38:40,020
What do you mean, a siren?

764
00:38:40,020 --> 00:38:41,380
Why would you say that about me?

765
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:42,420
We're at least

766
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:44,140
a power couple, right?

767
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:50,780
Look, Shanlifang is about to go public.

768
00:38:50,866 --> 00:38:53,100
That means Xinxin Vision's
Shanlifang stock options

769
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:53,980
can be cashed out.

770
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:55,500
Won't we be financially free then?

771
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,890
We won't have to worry about money.

772
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:58,060
So, at a time like this,

773
00:38:58,580 --> 00:39:00,140
if we don't get married and have a kid,

774
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:01,311
what are we waiting for?

775
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:04,180
So how many kids
are you planning to have?

776
00:39:04,933 --> 00:39:06,380
We'll let nature take its course.

777
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:08,580
Besides, even if we get married,

778
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:10,740
we'll still maintain
our current lifestyle.

779
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,420
Even if we have kids,

780
00:39:12,700 --> 00:39:15,260
we'll raise
and share the responsibilities together.

781
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:15,980
Right?

782
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:16,860
Absolutely.

783
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:42,460
My landlady won't let me down.

784
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:10,300
ظآزHey, you, you, you,
why is it you again?ظآز

785
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:14,630
ظآزAlways stumbling
upon my little secretsظآز

786
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:17,230
ظآزFalling on my brows, my lashesظآز

787
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:19,050
ظآزEven the strands by my mouthظآز

788
00:40:19,050 --> 00:40:21,910
ظآزLike my favorite kittenظآز

789
00:40:21,910 --> 00:40:23,720
ظآزOn a rainy spring afternoonظآز

790
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:28,380
ظآزHey, you, you, you,
why is it you again?ظآز

791
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:32,170
ظآزYou effortlessly
awaken my protective instinctsظآز

792
00:40:32,450 --> 00:40:34,590
ظآزHitting all my little thoughtsظآز

793
00:40:34,590 --> 00:40:36,510
ظآزMy doubts, and my temperظآز

794
00:40:36,790 --> 00:40:39,750
ظآزLike my favorite beer
and fried chicken in autumnظآز

795
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:42,200
(Pretentious Li)

796
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:44,500
(Special Assistant,
didn't you get off work early?)

797
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,300
(Where are you?)

798
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:46,420
(Qian Fei)

799
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:48,700
(I'm off work.
There's no Special Assistant.)

800
00:40:48,700 --> 00:40:49,740
(Pretentious Li)

801
00:40:49,740 --> 00:40:51,580
(I saw that you hadn't returned.)

802
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:53,380
(What if you don't get to eat dinner?)

803
00:40:53,580 --> 00:40:54,900
(I can't help but worry.)

804
00:40:55,044 --> 00:40:56,220
(Want to eat the food in the fridge?)

805
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:56,860
I'll use the restroom.

806
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:59,060
(Just say it. You know how to use
a microwave, right?)

807
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:28,940
Lu Ze.

808
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:32,020
You have to treat Jingjing well
from now on.

809
00:41:32,820 --> 00:41:33,500
Of course.

810
00:41:33,660 --> 00:41:35,100
Jingjing is a good girl.

811
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,950
Although she can be
a bit willful sometimes,

812
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:39,800
it's because her family didn't give
her enough of a sense of security.

813
00:41:40,977 --> 00:41:43,577
You must be more patient with her
about this in the future.

814
00:41:44,580 --> 00:41:46,260
The biggest benefit
of her marrying me

815
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:48,900
is that I can accept all her strengths
and weaknesses,

816
00:41:49,022 --> 00:41:50,866
as well as her theatrics
and insecurities.

817
00:41:51,420 --> 00:41:52,700
Such a humblebrag.

818
00:41:53,580 --> 00:41:54,180
By the way,

819
00:41:54,244 --> 00:41:56,340
the preparations
for Shanlifang's IPO have begun.

820
00:41:56,580 --> 00:41:58,380
We'll be analyzing simultaneously,

821
00:41:58,380 --> 00:41:59,500
including yours,

822
00:41:59,500 --> 00:42:01,800
the financial status
of all Shanlifang's subsidiaries.

823
00:42:02,020 --> 00:42:02,620
Is that so?

824
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:04,860
I don't know the specifics.

825
00:42:05,266 --> 00:42:07,180
I thought someone
would only come to oversee us

826
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:08,580
after a successful IPO.

827
00:42:09,540 --> 00:42:10,500
It's already started.

828
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:12,220
As I recall,

829
00:42:12,420 --> 00:42:14,100
I believe I've seen

830
00:42:14,100 --> 00:42:15,555
your company's financial statements.

831
00:42:15,660 --> 00:42:17,140
The numbers don't look good.

832
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:20,540
It seems a few recent financing rounds
have also failed.

833
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:23,933
It's true. The company is indeed
operating at a loss right now.

834
00:42:23,940 --> 00:42:25,390
But it's the early stage of a startup.

835
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:27,060
The product hasn't been
commercialized yet,

836
00:42:27,070 --> 00:42:28,288
and we need to keep investing.

837
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:29,377
So this is to be expected.

838
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:31,060
Three consecutive years of losses,

839
00:42:31,060 --> 00:42:32,666
and yet Shanlifang is still keeping you

840
00:42:32,711 --> 00:42:33,888
on board for their IPO.

841
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:34,900
It shows

842
00:42:35,460 --> 00:42:36,980
that they value you highly.

843
00:42:37,940 --> 00:42:40,060
They say capital is short-sighted,

844
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:41,860
but I feel quite lucky

845
00:42:42,220 --> 00:42:43,180
to have met Shanlifang.

846
00:42:43,288 --> 00:42:44,580
Chairman Liao is a good person.

847
00:42:44,580 --> 00:42:45,860
But I still think...

848
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:47,820
You're back.

849
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:50,580
Look how happy you are.

850
00:42:51,850 --> 00:42:54,340
You two must, absolutely must

851
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:55,420
be happy forever.

852
00:42:57,180 --> 00:42:58,220
Congratulations again.

853
00:42:58,422 --> 00:42:59,540
- Cheers.
- Come on.

854
00:43:01,100 --> 00:43:01,860
Cheers.

855
00:43:05,060 --> 00:43:06,860
=Love Has Fireworks=
(Next Episode Preview)

856
00:43:08,780 --> 00:43:09,300
Oh my god!

857
00:43:11,020 --> 00:43:11,850
What are you doing?

858
00:43:11,977 --> 00:43:13,933
Trying to scare me
and taking advantage of me.

859
00:43:14,380 --> 00:43:15,020
I heard

860
00:43:15,511 --> 00:43:17,555
that your joint sponsorship team
is in chaos.

861
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:19,820
And you still haven't found a solution.

862
00:43:20,200 --> 00:43:21,066
Here's the thing.

863
00:43:21,111 --> 00:43:23,390
I will definitely come up
with a plan as soon as possible.

864
00:43:23,420 --> 00:43:24,777
I'm just waiting for your word.

865
00:43:25,020 --> 00:43:27,390
Do you know why Ms. Fang
is giving you the cold shoulder?

866
00:43:28,060 --> 00:43:30,660
Whether Ms. Fang
accepts my apology or not,

867
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:32,660
I'm mentally prepared for it.

